                        <h2>Azure <small>Database for PostgreSQL</small></h2>
                        <h4>Trusted PostgreSQL Database services geared toward app developers</h4>
                        <em><a href="/pricing/1rmb-trial/" id="home_mysql_trial">Apply for 1RMB Trial<i class="icon icon-arrow-right-thin"></i></a></em> <a href="/pricing/pia/" id="home_mysql_pia">Buy Now<i class="icon icon-arrow-right-thin"></i></a>
