            <div class="pricing-page-section">
                <p>Azure Database for PostgreSQL delivers fully trusted, enterprise-ready community PostgreSQL database as a service. The PostgreSQL Community edition helps you easily move to the cloud using languages and frameworks of your choice. Most importantly, you will get built-in high availability and the capability to extend within seconds to help you easily adapt to changes in customer demands. In addition, you can benefit from unrivaled security and compliance, including Azure IP advantage and Azure’s industry leading business coverage. All these with a flexible pricing model so that you can choose the resources for your workload without any hidden cost.</p>
                <div class="cognitive-figure">
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <img role="presentation" src="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/css/images/postgresql-01-native-postgresql.png">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-9">
                        <h2>Community PostgreSQL that’s fully trusted</h2>
                        <p>Combine PostgreSQL community edition with the advantages of being a fully trusted service provider to easily manage infrastructure and database. Use Azure Database for PostgreSQL to get back to building your applications.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="cognitive-figure">
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <img role="presentation" src="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/css/images/postgresql-02-fav-lang.png">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-9">
                        <h2>Languages and frameworks of your choice</h2>
                        <p>Use popular open source frameworks and languages (including C#, C++, Java, Python, Node and PHP) to deliver a fully integrated experience to meet application development demands.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="cognitive-figure">
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <img role="presentation" src="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/css/images/postgresql-03-availability.png">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-9">
                        <h2>Built-in high availability</h2>
                        <p>Trust Azure to keep your enterprise applications running continuously. Azure Database for PostgreSQL offers high availability (99.99% SLA) to ensure your applications run as per normal when needed without extra configuration, replication or cost.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="cognitive-figure">
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <img role="presentation" src="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/css/images/postgresql-04-scale-on-the-fly.png">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-9">
                        <h2>Scale within seconds</h2>
                        <p>Provision within minutes and scale compute or storage with independence and flexibility within seconds.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="cognitive-figure">
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <img role="presentation" src="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/css/images/postgresql-05-rest-assured.png">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-9">
                        <h2>Unrivaled security and coverage</h2>
                        <p>Fully integrate into the Azure ecosystem to take advantage of Microsoft global network of datacenters, industry-leading security and round-the-clock monitoring capabilities.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="cognitive-figure">
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <img role="presentation" src="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/css/images/postgresql-06-pay-one-simple.png">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-9">
                        <h2>Simple and flexible pricing</h2>
                        <p>Enjoy everything you need with simple and flexible pricing, including capabilities such as automatic database patching, automatic backup, built-in monitoring and security, at no extra cost.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
